ile Victoria Bac\u0103u -->\n|win_MGH=  9|draw_MGH=  4|loss_MGH= 21|gf_MGH= 39|ga_MGH= 76 <!-- Minerul Gura Humorului -->\n|win_DUN=  9|draw_DUN=  2|loss_DUN= 23|gf_DUN= 37|ga_DUN= 56 <!-- Dun\u0103rea CSU Gala\u021bi -->\n|win_CMP=  6|draw_CMP=  4|loss_CMP= 24|gf_CMP= 21|ga_CMP= 81 <!-- Poiana C\u00e2mpina -->\n\n<!--Team notes-->\n\n<!--Team definitions (wikilinks in table)-->\n|name_SCV=[[CSM Suceava]]\n|name_IA\u0218=[[FC Politehnica Ia\u0219i (1945)|Politehnica Ia\u0219i]]\n|name_BR\u0102=[[ACS Dacia Unirea Br\u0103ila|Progresul Br\u0103ila]]\n|name_FCC=[[FC Farul Constan\u021ba|FC Constan\u021ba]]\n|name_MIZ=[[Steaua Mizil]]\n|name_FOC=[[CSM Foc\u0219ani|Unirea Dinamo Foc\u0219ani]]\n|name_USZ=[[AFC Unirea Slobozia|Unirea Slobozia]]\n|name_CEA=[[FC Ceahl\u0103ul Piatra Neam\u021b|Ceahl\u0103ul Piatra Neam\u021b]]\n|name_PA\u0218=[[CSM Pa\u0219cani|CFR Pa\u0219cani]]\n|name_ORS=[[CSM R\u00e2mnicu S\u0103rat|Olimpia R\u00e2mnicu S\u0103rat]]\n|name_PRA=[[Prahova Ploie\u0219ti|Prahova CSU Ploie\u0219ti]]\n|name_DEL=[[FC Delta Dobrogea Tulcea|Delta Dinamo Tulcea]]\n|name_FEPA=[[FEPA 74 B\u00e2rlad]]\n|name_BOT=[[CS Boto\u0219ani]]\n|name_AVB=[[CS Aerostar Bac\u0103u|Aripile Victoria Bac\u0103u]]\n|name_MGH=[[Minerul Gura Humorului]]\n|name_DUN=[[FCM Dun\u0103rea Gala\u021bi|Dun\u0103rea CSU Gala\u021bi]]\n|name_CMP=[[FCM C\u00e2mpina|Poiana C\u00e2mpina]]\n\n<!--Status-->\n|status_SCV=C,P\n|status_AVB=R\n|status_MGH=R\n|status_DUN=R\n|status_CMP=R\n\n<!--Table settings and rules-->\n|show_limit=7\n|class_rules=Rules for classification: 1) Points; 2) Goal difference; 3) Goals scored; 4) Head-to-head points; 5) Head-to-head goal difference; 6) Head-to-head goals scored; 7) Head-to-head away goals scored.\n\n<!--Qualification and relegation column definitions-->\n|res_col_header=PR\n|col_P=green1 |text_P=Promotion to [[1987\u201388 Divizia A|Divizia A]]\n|col_R=red1   |text_R=Relegation to [[Liga III|Divizia C]]\n}}\n\n===Serie II===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|styl